Comment.create(id: '1283', tool_id: '266', user_id: '9', is_pinned: '1', is_hidden: '0', index: '0', content: '<p>More information on TEXTPACK V and its use is available in the following:<br /><br />Alexa, Melina and Cornelia Zuell. \"Commonalities, differences and limitations of text analysis Software: The results of a review.\" <em>Zuma - Arbeitsbericht</em> (Jun. 1999). <a href=\"http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/abstracts/10192140/text-analysis-software-commonalities-difference-limitations-results-review\" target=\"_blank\">Web</a>.</p> <p>Olsen, Mark. \"Software Review: TEXTPACK V: Text Analysis Utilities for the Personal Computer.\" <em>Computers and the Humanities</em> 23.2 (1989):155-160. <a href=\"http://www.jstor.org/stable/30200155\" target=\"_blank\">Web</a>.</p>', updated_at: '2013-06-18 21:41:03', created_at: '2013-05-23 21:46:16', )
