ies</em> 10.6 (1976): 332. <a href=\"http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF02402556\" target=\"_blank\">Web</a>.</p> <p>Smith, John B. \"RATS: A Middle-Level Text Utility System.\" <em>Computers and the Humanities</em> 6.5 (1972): 277-283. <a href=\"http://www.jstor.org/stable/30199500\" target=\"_blank\">Web</a>.</p>', updated_at: '2014-07-21 17:07:15', created_at: '2013-05-24 22:01:23', )
