Comment.create(id: '1381', tool_id: '174', user_id: '9', is_pinned: '1', is_hidden: '0', index: '0', content: '<p>Hello rfd_0954,</p> <p>Thank you for your feedback. Could I trouble you for your input on how we could make it easier for you to find the links? TAPoR 2.5 can be contacted directly at <a href=\"mailto:tapor@ualberta.ca.\">tapor@ualberta.ca. </a></p> <p>At the moment, you can access ORBIS\'s homepage by clicking the thumbnail picture or the name of the tool. We\'ve also provided a direct link to its documentation, also from the tool\'s website. You can find this link at the top of the \'Documentation\' column, just below the image.</p> <p>Once you\'ve checked it out, we\'d love to have your impressions!</p>', updated_at: '2014-01-20 19:32:25', created_at: '2014-01-20 19:31:57', )
